{"tid":678124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"無論點都好，都會叫翻「馬鐵」同「西鐵」","createTime":"2018-05-25T20:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T02:52:50.000Z","uid":23107,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d90885703005b09cb4dbcf2219d900ec39c6fdae","tid":678124,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T20:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/041950_893a2a8cad58d49de4d92949ed564cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F041950_893a2a8cad58d49de4d92949ed564cd4.png&h=801ab9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似大多數新界人永遠將新界區嘅鐵路站叫做「火車站」<br />\n九龍同港島區嘅鐵路站叫做「地鐵站」一樣<br />\n永遠都改唔到口<br />\n<br />\n呢啲名雖然係已經成為歷史<br />\n但仍然一啲屬於大家對舊香港嘅集體回憶。<br />\n（00後嗰啲就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n同埋，點解我覺得「屯山線」會比「屯馬線」順口？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2aa84869bfcac6d379aede043e6fe5a0eee54a9","tid":678124,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T20:43:41.000Z","msg":"MTR 多鳩餘，叫返西鐵馬鐵咪得，牌都唔撚洗換<br />\n<br />\n以紅磡做分界，分兩程車行，可以順手留個空間畀西鐵再加到變9卡，至於馬鐵就冇得救"},{"pid":"f4dfcc8864e04119890b9117266bb5268f6995a5","tid":678124,"uid":29314,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T21:57:25.000Z","msg":"火車站、地鐵站先係正宗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等於巴士站、小巴站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你幾時會叫九巴站、城巴站、新巴站、潮聯站？"},{"pid":"35c5342cf34618ac0d94a561938946e5a6f30462","tid":678124,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T22:01:16.000Z","msg":"叫返kai子先係最正宗"},{"pid":"c135246d74e8dcf3e532a3e4fed0f41c001ef869","tid":678124,"uid":83371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T22:32:03.000Z","msg":"不如叫馬閪線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d42078e5a7510e570e9006184